trans-unit.source: The PropertySetAccessRule class represents a specific type of access rule that is used to allow or deny access to an Active Directory Domain Services property set.
trans-unit.target: PropertySetAccessRule 类表示特定类型的访问规则，用于允许或拒绝对 Active Directory 域服务属性集的访问。

trans-unit.source: For a list of property sets that are defined for Active Directory Domain Services, see the topic [Property Sets](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/property_sets.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).
trans-unit.target: 为 Active Directory 域服务定义的属性集的列表，请参阅主题[属性设置](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/property_sets.asp)在 MSDN 库中[http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.PropertySetAccessRule"></xref> class with the specified identity reference, access control type, property access type, and property set identifier.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.PropertySetAccessRule"></xref>使用指定的标识引用、 访问控制类型、 属性访问类型和属性集标识符的类。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Principal.IdentityReference"></xref> object that identifies the trustee of the access rule.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Security.Principal.IdentityReference"> </xref>对象，标识访问规则的受信者。

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.AccessControlType"></xref> enumeration values that specifies the access rule type.
trans-unit.target: 之一<xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.AccessControlType"></xref>指定访问规则类型的枚举值。

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.PropertyAccess"></xref> enumeration values that specifies the property access type.
trans-unit.target: 之一<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.PropertyAccess"></xref>枚举值，指定属性访问类型。

trans-unit.source: The Rights-Guid of the property set that this access rule applies to.
trans-unit.target: 此访问规则应用到的属性集权限 Guid。

trans-unit.source: In the Active Directory Domain Services schema documentation, this information can be found in the **Rights-GUID** row on the reference page for each property set.
trans-unit.target: 可以在 Active Directory 域服务架构文档中，找到此信息在**RIGHTS-GUID**每个属性集的引用页上的行。
